data.description: ***Seller will rebate buyer up to $3000 for NEW CARPET*** Enjoy the comfort and convenience of this beautiful home in Palm Coast, offerering a split bedroom plan with large rooms and plenty of natural light. You'll love the formal living room, the cozy family room, and the separate dining area. The home is well-built and has a huge back patio where you can relax and entertain. Your furry friends will appreciate the fenced in dog run that can be easily expanded. The home is tucked away in a peaceful and convenient neighborhood, close to I-95, shopping, restaurants, and more. Don't miss this amazing opportunity to own your dream home in Palm Coast! Schedule your private showing today!
